        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Competitor pools</span> — anyone can create a DAMM v2 pool for the same token with a lower fee. Aggregators will route to the cheapest pool</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">競爭對手池</span> — 任何人都可以為同一token創建費率更低嘅DAMM v2池。聚合器會路由到最平嘅池</span></li>
